data.description: Welcome Home. Cozy home on 1 acre Bradford county. Sit on the screened in front porch and sip your morning coffee. As you enter the front door you walk into the living area, with new flooring through out the entire home. Newly renovated from the floor up, new stove and refrigerator.  Out side is a large shop with two roll-up doors and concrete floors perfect for weekend projects. The septic is in great shape and recently pumped.
